    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1888-04-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1888-04-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="369" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d369">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Curry</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-04-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 21,
                            1888</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Has Cuban budget been presented to the Cortes, and does it contain Mora
                        claim?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bayard.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
